high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the sink.
Pick up the butterknife in the sink.
Turn to your left and face the white table with the bread on it.
Slice the bread with the butterknife.
Look downward to the white table.
Place the butterknife down on the table.
Look upward to the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right and move to face the microwave at the end of the counter.
Heat up the slice of bread in the microwave and take the bread slice out when finished.
Turn left and go back to the white table.
Place the heated bread slice on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a slice of bread and place on the white table.

high_descs: Turn left to face sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around walk to table turn right to face table.
Slice half of the bread loaf.
Look down at the table.
Place knife on the bread.
Look straight ahead over the table.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right, walk to microwave, left to face the microwave.
Open microwave, place bread in, close door, heat for 3 seconds, remove bread.
Turn left walk to table, turn right to face table.
Place bread on table next to the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Slice bread, heat it up and serve.

high_descs: Make a left to face the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Make a left to walk to the white table with the loaf of bread on it.
Slice the loaf of bread with the knife.
Turn to face the table.
Put the knife down on the table.
Turn to face the bread on the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right to walk to towards the microwave.
Warm up the slice of bread in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Make a left to walk to the table.
Put the slice of bread down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of bread in the microwave, setting it down on the table.
